Interface SelectionInputDialogPrimitive

All Superinterfaces:
InputPrimitive, Primitive
public interface SelectionInputDialogPrimitive extends InputPrimitive
An interface representing a selection dialog (SD) primitive.

This primitive has type Primitive.PrimitiveType.SD.

The allowed input format is InputPrimitive.InputFormat.FIXED.
